# Comets Studio – Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
Comets Studio is an AI-powered component and app builder. Local-first, private, with Ollama as the primary AI engine. Think "local v0" or "Replit-style templates."

## Architecture
- **Chat**: Zustand store (`lib/stores/chat-store.ts`), messages with optional `projectFiles`
- **AI**: `lib/ai-service.ts` – multi-provider (Ollama, DeepSeek, Kimi, etc.)
- **Templates**: `lib/templates.ts` (components), `lib/project-templates.ts` (full projects)
- **Deploy/Export**: `lib/vercel-deploy.ts` – Vercel deploy, ZIP export (Replit-ready)
- **Preview**: Sandpack in `components/code-playground/CodePlayground.tsx`

## Key Conventions
- **Design**: Slate/gray palette, no glassmorphism, Lucide icons, Tailwind
- **Components**: Clean, minimal, accessible (ARIA, focus states)
- **Code gen**: Always output runnable `tsx` in code blocks

## File Tree
- `components/file-tree.tsx` – sidebar for multi-file projects
- `components/code-playground/CodePlayground.tsx` – Sandpack + FileTree when `projectFiles`
- `components/chat/chat-interface.tsx` – main chat UI, template/project integration

## When Adding Features
- Use existing AI providers; add new ones in `lib/ai-service.ts`
- Project templates go in `lib/project-templates.ts`
- Deploy/export use `buildProjectFilesRaw` or `buildProjectFilesFromTemplate`
